# Changelog

## [1.08]
### Added
 - 2022-11-06
  - pokemon loading

## [1.07]
### Added
 - 2022-10-28
  - added pokedex parsing
  - added pokedex printing
### Updated
 - 2022-10-28

## [1.06]
### Added
 - 2022-10-20
  - added class for map
  - added class for character
  - added class for player
  - added class for trainer
  - added class for world
  - refactored old code for cpp
  - added fly command
  - added player movement between maps
### Updated
 - 2022-10-20

## [1.05]
### Added
 - 2022-10-16
  - added support for ncurses map printing
  - added ncurses unbuffered input
  - added player movement with ncurses input
 - 2022-10-18
  - added trainer battles menu
  - added trainer list menu
  - added pokecenter/pokemart menu
### Updated
 - 2022-10-16

## [1.04]
### Added
 - 2022-09-26
  - added utility and trainer files to organize new features
 - 2022-10-02
  - created heap for player next move storage
  - wrote function for getting the next movement position of a trainer
### Updated
 - 2022-09-26
  - changed the map to keep track of trainers

## [1.03]
### Added
 - 2022-09-16
  - implemented sheaffer's code for map generation
### Updated
 - 2022-09-16
  - changed user input to be simpler and fit new coordinates

## [1.02]
### Added
 - 2022-09-11
  - added data structures for maps, and a variable to hold a 2d array of maps making the world
  - added functions to get maps from the world, and generate new if they dont exit, connecting neighbor paths
  - added terminal input to move from one map to another (n,s,e,w)
 - 2022-09-13
  - added terminal input to fly to other maps with boundary checking for all input
### Updated
 - 2022-09-13
  - fixed how pointers are passed for simplicity in map get and generation
  - updated user input flow and logic
 - 2022-09-14
  - updated terrain generation
  - updated pokemart and pokecenter generation to have a chance to spawn

